      • addSub

        public boolean addSub(CIdentity frameId,
                      CIdentity subFrameId)
        Adds a new sub-frame relationship for a frame that has been previously added, either as the root-frame or, via this method, as a sub-frame. The specified sub-frame may or may not have been previously added.
        Parameters:
        frameId - Identity of existing frame
        subFrameId - Identity of sub-frame of existing frame
        Returns:
        True if sub-frame has not been previously added
        Throws:
        uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon_util.KAccessException - if frame to which sub-frame is to added not present in hierarchy
